=head1 NAME

VBoxAdm::Utils - Common Mail Handling utils.

=head1 VERSION

This documentation refers to VBoxAdm::Utils version @VERSION@
built on @BUILDDATE@.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    use VBoxAdm::Utils;
